                    "Compare the Q-value of the fission reaction (U-235) to the combustion of methane (ΔH = −890 kJ/mol = −9.2 eV per molecule)",
                    "Express the ratio: how many times more energy does fission release per atom than chemical combustion?",
                    "Calculate the mass of U-235 required to produce the same energy as burning 1 kg of coal (ΔH_coal ≈ 32 MJ/kg)",
