                "The r-process site was uncertain until the 2017 gravitational wave detection GW170817 confirmed neutron star mergers as a major r-process site",
                "The Bethe-Weizsäcker semi-empirical mass formula overestimates BE/A for very light nuclei (A<12) and near magic numbers"
