        purpose: "Derive the Lawson criterion from energy balance arguments, calculate nτT for a range of historical and current fusion experiments, plot the Lawson diagram, identify the optimum temperature for D-T fusion, and compare the triple product approaches of magnetic confinement (ITER) and inertial confinement (NIF).",
