        purpose: "Calculate the Lorentz factor for cosmic ray muons, derive the time-dilated half-life, predict the sea-level muon flux from altitude measurements with and without time dilation, compare to Frisch-Smith experimental data, and interpret the same calculation from the muon's rest frame using length contraction.",
