                    "Allow the lamp to warm up for 2 minutes to reach steady output",
                    "Measure and record background illuminance with the lamp off — subtract this from all readings",
                    "Set distance r = 0.10 m — record the lux meter reading (it will be very high)",
                    "Increase r in steps: 0.10, 0.15, 0.20, 0.25, 0.30, 0.40, 0.50, 0.60, 0.80, 1.00, 1.20, 1.50 m",
