        purpose: "Calculate decay constants and activities for members of the uranium-238 decay chain; determine the secular equilibrium condition; calculate the time to reach equilibrium; apply the Bateman equation for daughter activity growth; analyse the Mo-99/Tc-99m generator used in nuclear medicine",
