            "Prostate cancer: ⁶⁸Ga-PSMA PET has become the preferred staging tool for prostate cancer, replacing conventional imaging in many centres",
            "Thyroid cancer therapy: ¹³¹I remains the standard treatment for differentiated thyroid cancer, exploiting thyroid iodine uptake",
