            "Signal generator and amplifier (to provide stable, constant-level sound source)",
            "Calibrated sound level meter (Class 2 or better, reading to ±1 dB)",
            "Metre ruler and tape measure (0–4 m)",
            "Open space (school hall, sports hall, or outdoor area away from reflecting surfaces)",
            "Retort stand (to hold sound level meter at constant height)",
