                    "Add a carpet offcut covering half the floor — measure RT60",
                    "Add curtains along one wall — measure RT60",
                    "Each time, record total added absorbing area and calculate new total A",
                    "Predict RT60 from Sabine's formula: RT60 = 0.161V/A",
                    "Compare predicted to measured RT60 for each configuration"
