                    "Record L₂",
                    "If the tube is long enough, find the third resonance at L₃ ≈ 5λ/4 and record L₃",
                    "The difference L₂ − L₁ = λ/2 (this difference eliminates the end correction)",
                    "Therefore: λ = 2(L₂ − L₁)",
