            "The pinhole needle is sharp — handle carefully and store in a cork when not in use",
            "Latex balloons can burst unexpectedly — do not over-inflate beyond manufacturer guidance",
            "CO₂ from dry ice can cause cold burns — handle dry ice with insulated gloves",
