                "Ratio of deflation rates approximates √(M_CO₂/M_He) = √(44/4) ≈ 3.32 — lighter gas escapes ~3.3× faster",
                "Deflation curves are steepest early (when pressure difference is greatest) and flatten as balloon approaches ambient pressure",
