            "Ammonia source (concentrated ammonia, soaked cotton wool, sealed at one end of the tube)",
            "Indicator paper or pH indicator in the tube (to track ammonia diffusion front)",
            "Alternatively: use coloured gas tracer (bromine water or iodine vapour) and observe coloured front movement",
